Basic Syntax of Selenium code to open the browser automatically ; 
1 -> Create a Maven Project 
2 -> In the SRC file of that project , get into the pom.xml file 
3 -> In that file add dependencies of selenium that imports all the packages required 


Basic code for opening browser - 

import org.openqa.selenium.WebDriver ;
import org.openqa.selemium.chrome.ChromeDriver ; 

public class prog1 {
  public static void main (String[] args){

    WebDriver  driver = new ChromeDriver();
    driver.get("URL of the Website to be opened") ; 
    driver.close(); 
  }
}

